{"pageProps":{"postData":{"_id":"5fb664b19f9e7f16fd3246f4","id":"dotignore","crawlTimestamp":"19/11/2020 12:27:27","packageName":"dotignore","description":"ignorefile/includefile matching .gitignore spec","repository":{"type":"git","url":"git+ssh://git@github.com/bmeck/dotignore.git"},"readme":"# dotignore\n\n## `ignored $IGNOREFILE`\n\nCheck the ignorefile against the current directory.\nPrint out if a file should be ignored by prefixing with a `-`.\nIf the file should not be ignored prefix it with a `+`.\n\n## API\n\n### exports.createMatcher(str)\n\nReturn a `Matcher` that fully matches the `str` argument.\n\n`str` should conform to the `.gitignore` specification.\n\n### Matcher.shouldIgnore(name)\n\nTest that all the rules provided to create the matcher match the name given.\n`/` is expected as the path delimiter.\nReturns `true` if the name should be ignored.\n\n## LICENSE\n\nMIT\n\n","homepage":"https://github.com/bmeck/dotignore#readme","trustScore":12,"sourceRank":{"basic_info_present":1,"repository_present":1,"readme_present":1,"license_present":1,"versions_present":1,"follows_semver":1,"recent_release":0,"not_brand_new":1,"one_point_oh":0,"dependent_projects":2,"dependent_repositories":0,"stars":1,"contributors":1,"subscribers":1,"all_prereleases":0,"any_outdated_dependencies":0,"is_deprecated":0,"is_unmaintained":0,"is_removed":0,"trustScore":12},"versions":[{"versionNumber":"0.0.0","timestamp":"2013-02-22T19:02:20.830Z","trustScore":5,"dependencies":[{"packageName":"minimatch","version":"~0.2.9"}]},{"versionNumber":"0.0.1","timestamp":"2014-03-10T07:12:20.950Z","trustScore":6,"dependencies":[{"packageName":"minimatch","version":"~0.2.9"}]},{"versionNumber":"0.1.0","timestamp":"2014-08-10T17:56:24.055Z","trustScore":6,"dependencies":[{"packageName":"minimatch","version":"~1.0.0"}]},{"versionNumber":"0.1.1","timestamp":"2014-08-19T07:00:34.876Z","trustScore":6,"dependencies":[{"packageName":"minimatch","version":"~1.0.0"}]},{"versionNumber":"0.1.2","timest